<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Confirmation de commande</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #2c738a;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #3a96a3;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        h2 {
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
        }
        p {
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .order-info {
            display: block;
            width: fit-content;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #245263;
            color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .footer-email {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .footer-email p {
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .footer-email a {
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Confirmation de commande</h2>
        <p>Voici les détails de votre commande :</p>
        <span class="order-info">
            ID de commande: <%= order._id %><br>
            Nom du cours: <%= order.name %><br>
            Prix: <%= order.price %>dh<br>
            Date de commande: <%= order.date %>
        </span>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-email">
        <p>Si vous avez des questions, n'hésitez pas à nous contacter à <a href="mailto:dacademy.sup1@gmail.com">dacademy.sup1@gmail.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
